## QXB 上传

- 审核页：`QXB_REVIEW_PORT=8789 node work/qxb-agent/review_server.js` → http://127.0.0.1:8789/review
- 确认上传 → 异步队列 `reports/qxb-review-upload-queue.json`
- 失败常见原因：VIN decode (`getApprovedVinFact`)、429 限流（白名单 IP）
- 行号 ↔ 库存：Pending 看 QXBxxxx；已批准现网看 HC25xxxx
- Runbook：`data/knowledge-base/qxb-batch-upload-runbook.md`

## Python 环境

- 优先：`.venv-qxb/bin/python3`（pipeline 依赖）或 `.venv/bin/python3`
- 勿用系统 python3（缺 openpyxl/PIL/dotenv）

## 销售数据

- 业务数据问题：`python -m truth.verified_sales_intelligence "问题"`，勿猜数字

